sentence: Trump for President Campaign has just announced it will be in Wichita Kansas for a major rally on Saturday prior to the Caucus
Trump will also be speaking at the Kansas Caucus and then departing for Orlando Florida to speak to a crowd of approximately 20000 people or more
Because of this he will not be able to speak at CPAC as he has done for many consecutive years
Trump would like to thank Matt Schlapp and all of the executives at CPAC and looks forward to returning to next year hopefully as President of the United States
